In my case, the need to change the queryset ModelChoiceField of Formsets, according to the user's region.
I managed to solve this:

```
class MatriculaInicialInline(InlineFormSet):
    model = Matricula
    extra = 1
    form_class = MatriculaForm

    def get_factory_kwargs(self):
        kwargs = super(MatriculaInicialInline, self).get_factory_kwargs()

        def get_field_qs(field, **kwargs):
            formfield = field.formfield(**kwargs)
            if field.name == 'pessoa':
                formfield.queryset = Pessoa.objects.filter(pessoa__matricula__isnull=True)
            if field.name == 'user':
                formfield.initial = self.request.user
            return formfield

        kwargs.update({
            'formfield_callback': get_field_qs
        })
        return kwargs
```

